The TDD cycle is complete. All 8 tests implemented and passing:

1. ✅ No commands → returns initial position and heading
2. ✅ F facing N → moves north (y+1)
3. ✅ F facing E → moves east (x+1)
4. ✅ F facing S → moves south (y-1)
5. ✅ F facing W → moves west (x-1)
6. ✅ L from N → rotates to W
7. ✅ R from N → rotates to E
8. ✅ Multiple commands in sequence (FRF: move north, rotate right, move east)
